  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "It's not always easy, it's not always easy To put your, to put your hate down And your love up, it's not always easy Taking your advice, no it's not always easy To take your own advice Are you listening? Are you listening? You are still human, you still got feelings You still got some bruises, your heart needs to be broken It's not always easy To take your own advice Heart over eyes, it's not always easy You're still human, you're still human Anxiety is crushing me, it's rocking my brain I don't understand my name, I don't understand the game Hurts too much to remain the same Hurts too much to go and have another way I don't know if I can think, I don't know if I should talk All these things make me wanna walk away Or do I, do I die today? Or if I stay are you okay? Am I still human if I feel this way? When I feel this way Am I still human? Am I still human? You still had a bad day, you may know what to say But it's not always easy Taking your own advice Yeah it's not always easy Heart over eyes It's not always easy Taking your own advice Heart over eyes You know what to say You know what is right You know what it means It's always been the best interest on some good file Yeah It's not always easy",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 7.420000076293945,
      "text": "It's not always easy, it's not always easy",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 15.720000267028809,
      "text": "To put your, to put your hate down",
      "start": 7.71999979019165
    },
    {
      "end": 20.8799991607666,
      "text": "And your love up, it's not always easy",
      "start": 15.720000267028809
    },
    {
      "end": 28.5,
      "text": "Taking your advice, no it's not always easy",
      "start": 22
    },
    {
      "end": 35.79999923706055,
      "text": "To take your own advice",
      "start": 31.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 40.2400016784668,
      "text": "Are you listening? Are you listening?",
      "start": 35.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 47.47999954223633,
      "text": "You are still human, you still got feelings",
      "start": 40.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 57.08000183105469,
      "text": "You still got some bruises, your heart needs to be broken",
      "start": 48.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 67.18000030517578,
      "text": "It's not always easy",
      "start": 58.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 77.5199966430664,
      "text": "To take your own advice",
      "start": 71.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 84.27999877929688,
      "text": "Heart over eyes, it's not always easy",
      "start": 77.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 98.33999633789062,
      "text": "You're still human, you're still human",
      "start": 90.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 101.68000030517578,
      "text": "Anxiety is crushing me, it's rocking my brain",
      "start": 98.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 105.66000366210938,
      "text": "I don't understand my name, I don't understand the game",
      "start": 101.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 108.66000366210938,
      "text": "Hurts too much to remain the same",
      "start": 105.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 113.16000366210938,
      "text": "Hurts too much to go and have another way",
      "start": 109.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 116.95999908447266,
      "text": "I don't know if I can think, I don't know if I should talk",
      "start": 113.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 120.36000061035156,
      "text": "All these things make me wanna walk away",
      "start": 117.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 122.18000030517578,
      "text": "Or do I, do I die today?",
      "start": 120.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 124.41999816894531,
      "text": "Or if I stay are you okay?",
      "start": 122.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 128.24000549316406,
      "text": "Am I still human if I feel this way?",
      "start": 125.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 132.33999633789062,
      "text": "When I feel this way",
      "start": 129.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 135.9600067138672,
      "text": "Am I still human?",
      "start": 133.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 138.94000244140625,
      "text": "Am I still human?",
      "start": 137.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 148.3000030517578,
      "text": "You still had a bad day, you may know what to say",
      "start": 141.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 151.82000732421875,
      "text": "But it's not always easy",
      "start": 148.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 155.8800048828125,
      "text": "Taking your own advice",
      "start": 152.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 160.9600067138672,
      "text": "Yeah it's not always easy",
      "start": 157.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 164.17999267578125,
      "text": "Heart over eyes",
      "start": 161.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 169.83999633789062,
      "text": "It's not always easy",
      "start": 165.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 176.22000122070312,
